{"id": "1422550462552477859", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "993426658881196032", "author_name": "bgm0001", "author_bot": false, "content": "真上にある", "timestamp": "2025-09-30T11:47:39.982000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1422552474740457472", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "430590295659249664", "author_name": "kumada_chinatu", "author_bot": false, "content": "8回攻撃ネズミ突撃を作る。(可能なら抜く？) 次のターン超次元に入れる。\nカーシアとか使ってうまいこと超次元に3枚ぐらい貯める？\n超次元空間入ったらダフォキーとか使って威力上げて殴る。\n\nであってますかね・・・？", "timestamp": "2025-09-30T11:55:39.725000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1422555266754281502", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "993426658881196032", "author_name": "bgm0001", "author_bot": false, "content": "そんな感じでいいと思います！\n正直、最高瞬間火力とか最適解とか完璧とか求めないのであれば、ある程度雑に扱ったって強いです。\n8回に固執していたらダメ抑えられないと思うし\n再収納できないことと、ターン始めに収納する点だけ気を付けていれば大丈夫かと\n(もちろんジェンキンに限らず、超次元突入や怒濤に合わせてありとあらゆるバフを乗せるのは定石)", "timestamp": "2025-09-30T12:06:45.393000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1422556181028671641", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 19, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "今はジェンキンだけだとどうしても暇なターンが発生しやすくなったのが注意点です", "timestamp": "2025-09-30T12:10:23.373000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["430590295659249664"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1422552474740457472", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1422556340991033404", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "その為、ダフォダイルが穴を埋めて狂気解放したり千変万化を超次元にしまったり取り出したりします", "timestamp": "2025-09-30T12:11:01.511000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1422556445110440047", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "首かりも1000〜2000ダメージくらいでます", "timestamp": "2025-09-30T12:11:26.335000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1422558099054530672", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "430590295659249664", "author_name": "kumada_chinatu", "author_bot": false, "content": "ダフォも首刈りが来ないとうまく動けないとかをお互い補い合う感じなんですね… ありがとうございます", "timestamp": "2025-09-30T12:18:00.666000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1422558377598386296", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "ダフォは狂気解放がバカ強いのでそれで埋めていきます", "timestamp": "2025-09-30T12:19:07.076000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
